summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 10.6°C), outside temperature (down 9.3°C), and inside temperature (down 3.6°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 6%).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 7505 lux) and cloud levels (up 470 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 7949 lux), dew point temperature (up 9.3°C), outside temperature (up 10.5°C), and cloud levels (up 449 m) when compared to today.
